at the same time, strangely musical. Many will feel that, in this later work, these qualities have been enhanced and that Garrett’s advancing maturity indicates strongly that his early promise will be richly fulfilled.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aAmerican poetryy20th century. 7aPOETRY / General.2bisacsh1 aDowns, Jo Alys, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.7560/73380040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292772854423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292772854/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles